summary:
This is natural style ENB.
It is the ENB, which is setting in for Pure Weather.
Required:Pure Weather, Recommend:Pure Water
descriptionHtml:
☆★☆ [font=book antiqua][color=#33CCFF][size=7]Toric law of nature ENB[/size][/color][/font] ☆★☆

This is natural and realistic style ENB.
It is the[size=2] ENB,[/size] which is setting in for Pure Weather.
In addition, I recommend installation of Pure Waters.
Because,set to Water and UnderWater of enbseries.ini for Pure Water.


[color=hotpink][size=3]! Important ![/size][/color]
[color=gold]This ENB is for Pure Weather-Realism.[/color]
Therefore,Under the situation of Pure Weather-Brighter Nights Edition, it will be that an image changes.
About Toric law of nature ENB-N. Even if it is Pure Weather-Brighter Night Edition, it will be all right.But I am unconfirmed,sorry...

[Required]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52423/?]Pure Weather-Realism[/url]

[Recommend]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1111/?]Pure Waters[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1111/?]
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60576/?]Pure waters - Waterfalls[/url]

[Recommend for more reality weather]
[color=gold][color=gold]By this ENB, skin come to wet get in a rainy day, this is t[/color]he greatest feature.[/color]
Let's make more realistic expression!
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/19660/?]Get Snowy[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15506/?]Lightning during Thunder Storms[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25666/?]Rainbows[/url]
If you use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52612/?]Real Shelter[/url] mod...
Open enbseries.ini
Please write it as follows.
[RAIN]
Enable=false



---[font=book antiqua][color=lightskyblue][size=7]Installation[/size][/color][/font]---

[color=gold][size=4]1.Set to Game and Graphic card drivers.[/size][/color]
a) SkyrimPrefs.ini
　 . bTreesReceiveShadows=1
　 . bDrawLandShadows=1
　 . bFloatPointRenderTarget=1
b) Turn off antialiasing and anisotropic filtering in game options menu or graphic card drivers.


[color=gold][size=4]2.Open the Main Files.[/size][/color]
a) Copy all files and folders of the Main Files.
b) Paste all files and folders to your Skyrim install folder. (the same place as the skyrim.exe. Steam/SteamApps/common/Skyrim)


[color=gold][size=4]3.Download [color=white]Latest[/color] [url=http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html]ENBSeries[/url][/size][/color]
a) Get to enbseries_skyrim_v0xxx_zip
b) Open the WrapperVersion folder and copy d3d9.dll and enbhost.exe
c) Paste d3d9.dll and enbhost.exe to your Skyrim install folder. (the same place as the skyrim.exe. Steam/SteamApps/common/Skyrim)


[color=gold][size=4]4.Dwonload [url=http://www.dev-c.com/skyrim/enbhelper]Skyrim ENB Helper[/url] (Toric law of nature ENB-B only)[/size][/color]
a) Copy enbhelper.dll
b) Paste enbhelper.dll in enbseries folder.


[color=gold][size=4]5.ENB Patch[/size][/color]
[url=http://enbseries.enbdev.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=1499]Skyrim particle patch for ENB[/url]
a) Download PARTICLE PATCH ALL-IN-ONE
b) Install PARTICLE PATCH ALL-IN-ONE in NMM etc..


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[size=3]Last,If possible...[/size]
You open the enblocal file.
[MEMORY]
ExpandSystemMemoryX64=true ← If your PC's OS is 32bit,Write "false"
VideoMemorySizeMb=0 ← Write VRAM of Your PC. But, In v264, this operation is not necessary!
--an example--
If VRAM 1024MB...
VideoMemorySizeMb=1014 ← [-10] better!
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------




[color=gold][size=4]For high quality visual[/size][/color]
ini setting ---->       [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10853/?]Skyrim True Ultra Settings[/url] or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51033/?]EWIs High SkyrimPrefs and inis[/url]
LOD          ---->       [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52901/?]Skyrim High Definition LODs[/url]
Grass Tree --->        [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59774/?]Tamriel Reloaded Grass - Plants - shrubs[/url] + [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32246/?]Ultimate Lush Overhaul[/url] or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/141/?]Skyrim Flora Overhaul[/url]
Texture     --->        [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/607/?]Skyrim HD - 2K Textures[/url] etc, HD texture mods
Interior lightning --> [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30450/?]Realstic Lighting Overhaul[/url], other interior lightning mods / not use weather.esp
Scene of the town -> Towns and Villages Enhanced_series / Example [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20185/?]Towns and Villages Enhanced-Reften[/url]
